you're scared of them.

1282
01:29:24.442 --> 01:29:26.611
Silly, only grown-up men
are scared of women.

1283
01:29:26.694 --> 01:29:28.863
I think the men look beautiful.

1284
01:29:28.946 --> 01:29:30.865
How would you know?

1285
01:29:47.924 --> 01:29:51.344
-Liesl, who are you dancing with?
-Nobody.

1286
01:29:52.804 --> 01:29:54.472
