It's an Austrian folk dance.

1294
01:30:24.460 --> 01:30:25.837
Show me.

1295
01:30:25.920 --> 01:30:28.339
Oh, Kurt, I haven't danced that
since I was a little girl.

1296
01:30:28.423 --> 01:30:30.425
Oh, you remember.
Please?

1297
01:30:30.508 --> 01:30:32.552
-Well...
-Please.

1298
01:30:32.635 --> 01:30:35.138
All right. Come on over here.

1299
