Now you bow, and I curtsy.

1300
01:30:39.183 --> 01:30:40.435
-Like this?
-Fine.

1301
01:30:40.518 --> 01:30:41.894
Now we go for a little walk. This way.

1302
01:30:41.978 --> 01:30:45.106
One, two, three.
One, two, three.

1303
01:30:45.189 --> 01:30:47.483
One, two, three.
Step together.

1304
01:30:47.567 --> 01:30:49.944
Now, step, hop. Step, hop.

1305
01:30:50.027 --> 01:30:52.363
-Now, turn under.
-(grunts)

1306
01:30:52.447 --> 01:30:55.450
Not quite.
This way. Hop, step, hop.

1307
01:30:55.533 --> 01:30:57.452
And under.

1308
01:30:57.535 --> 01:31:00.580
-Kurt, we'll have to practice.
-Um, do allow me, will you?

1309
01:31:00.663 --> 01:31:02.498
Mm-hm.

1310
01:32:28.960 --> 01:32:30.836
I don't remember any more.

1311
01:32:33.339 --> 01:32:35.341
-Your face is all red.
-Is it?

1312
01:32:37.134 --> 01:32:39.303
I don't suppose I'm used to dancing.

1313
01:32:39.387 --> 01:32:41.138
(applause)

1314
01:32:41.222 --> 01:32:43.599
That was beautifully done.

1315
01:32:43.683 --> 01:32:46.018
What a lovely couple you make.

1316
01:32:46.102 --> 01:32:48.604
Yes. I think it's time
the children said good night.

1317
01:32:48.688 --> 01:32:51.399
Yes, we'll be in the hall in a moment.
We've got something very special prepared.

1318
01:32:51.482 --> 01:32:52.650
-Right?
-BRIGITTA: Right.

1319
01:32:52.733 --> 01:32:54.735
-(all chattering)
-MARIA: Yes, come on!

1320
01:33:01.200 --> 01:33:03.869
