find a friend at the party.

1322
01:33:09.709 --> 01:33:11.586
A bit chilly out tonight, isn't it?

1323
01:33:11.669 --> 01:33:13.671
Oh, I don't know.

1324
01:33:13.754 --> 01:33:16.048
It seemed rather warm to me.

1325
01:33:16.132 --> 01:33:18.593
