<i>♪ Or childhood ♪</i>

1842
02:13:03.141 --> 02:13:06.186
<i>♪ I must have done ♪</i>

1843
02:13:06.269 --> 02:13:10.107
<i>♪ Something ♪</i>

1844
02:13:10.190 --> 02:13:12.651
<i>♪ Good ♪</i>

1845
02:13:12.734 --> 02:13:18.073
Do you know when I first
started loving you?

1846
02:13:18.156 --> 02:13:21.868
That night at the dinner table
when you sat on that ridiculous pine cone.

1847
02:13:21.952 --> 02:13:25.330
-(laughing)
-What? (laughs)

1848
02:13:25.414 --> 02:13:28.166
I knew the first time
you blew that silly whistle.

1849
02:13:29.710 --> 02:13:31.670
Oh, my love.

1850
02:13:35.757 --> 02:13:38.093
<i>♪ For here you are ♪</i>

1851
02:13:38.176 --> 02:13:40.303
<i>♪ Standing there ♪</i>

1852
02:13:40.387 --> 02:13:43.598
<i>♪ Loving me ♪</i>

1853
02:13:45.475 --> 02:13:49.021
<i>♪ Whether or not ♪</i>

1854
