<i>♪ I must have done ♪</i>

1858
02:14:02.784 --> 02:14:07.956
<i>♪ Something good ♪</i>

1859
02:14:09.666 --> 02:14:13.545
BOTH:<i> ♪ Nothing comes from nothing ♪</i>

1860
02:14:13.628 --> 02:14:17.132
<i>♪ Nothing ever could ♪</i>

1861
