<i>♪ So somewhere in my youth ♪</i>

1862
02:14:23.138 --> 02:14:25.057
(chuckling)
<i>♪ Or childhood ♪</i>

1863
02:14:28.435 --> 02:14:31.730
<i>♪ I must have done ♪</i>

1864
02:14:31.813 --> 02:14:34.900
<i>♪ Something ♪</i>

1865
02:14:37.152 --> 02:14:42.449
<i>♪ Something ♪</i>

1866
02:14:45.368 --> 02:14:49.498
<i>♪ Good ♪</i>

1867
02:14:56.338 --> 02:14:59.257
-Maria.
-Hmm.

1868
02:14:59.341 --> 02:15:03.512
Is there anyone I should go to
to ask permission to marry you?

1869
02:15:08.308 --> 02:15:10.977
-Well, why don't we ask the children?
-The children?

1870
02:15:11.061 --> 02:15:15.440
(church bells tolling)

1871
02:15:24.324 --> 02:15:27.828
(tolling continues)

1872
02:15:47.180 --> 02:15:50.976
(tolling continues)

1873
02:15:57.691 --> 02:16:01.403
(organ playing)

1874
02:16:01.486 --> 02:16:04.656
(organ continues)

1875
02:16:59.377 --> 02:17:03.840
NUNS:<i> ♪ How do you solve</i>
<i>a problem like Maria ♪</i>

1876
02:17:03.924 --> 02:17:08.553
<i>♪ How do you catch</i>
<i>a cloud and pin it down ♪</i>

1877
02:17:08.637 --> 02:17:13.099
<i>♪ How do you find a word</i>
<i>that means Maria ♪</i>

1878
